{"tid":165383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"火焰之紋章 fire emblem heros (11)","createTime":"2017-03-21T10:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T11:12:42.000Z","uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd015bf56918df66cc52fe44509b6eeca8f2c374","tid":165383,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"火焰之紋章Heros 開post template<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">新Post Template:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=198aedbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wkveQBRYrdlRzxQdiAi-zS7jw5nhKnxMcf9oleTMsdY/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C2fXORaUoAEovwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC2fXORaUoAEovwu.jpg&h=557d625c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\nPV: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCtFNO9ULdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcCtFNO9ULdc&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=2fc3ce8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cCtFNO9ULdc</a><br />\n官網: <a href=\"https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffire-emblem-heroes.com%2Fja%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a53db868\" target=\"_blank\">https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/</a><br />\n系統: <a href=\"https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/system/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffire-emblem-heroes.com%2Fja%2Fsystem%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7136df24\" target=\"_blank\">https://fire-emblem-heroes.com/ja/system/</a><br />\n官方Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FE_Heroes_JP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFE_Heroes_JP&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b7cb700e\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FE_Heroes_JP</a><br />\n部份參戰角色:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjaMV1RwR_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfjaMV1RwR_8&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=fce1d1da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjaMV1RwR_8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dcUN53lWbA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdcUN53lWbA4&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ddb5f8fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dcUN53lWbA4</a><br />\n攻略WIKI:<br />\n<a href=\"http://altema.jp/fe-heroes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Ffe-heroes%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=006fb457\" target=\"_blank\">http://altema.jp/fe-heroes/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://fe-heroes.gamerch.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffe-heroes.gamerch.com%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cff2168a\" target=\"_blank\">https://fe-heroes.gamerch.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://appmedia.jp/fe-heroes-wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fappmedia.jp%2Ffe-heroes-wiki&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=34773aa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://appmedia.jp/fe-heroes-wiki</a><br />\n此GAME因為全球同SER<br />\n所以會到香港時間<span style=\"color: red;\">每日下午3點</span>先拎到Login Bonus同回復對戰權<br />\n<strong>改名改語言:<br />\n去FAQ改<br />\n勳章獲得方法:</strong><br />\n修練之塔1-5/F<br />\n<strong>大勳章獲得方法:</strong><br />\n修練之塔6-10/F<br />\n<strong>英雄之翼獲得方法:</strong><br />\n打鬥技場取得<br />\n每日去搵主頁有心心嘅角色講野拎到5條<br />\n好友list打招呼拎到5條<br />\n好友list有5人以上時打招呼送多5條<br />\n賣角色:<br />\n1星5條<br />\n2星10條<br />\n3星150條<br />\n4星300條<br />\n5星1000條<br />\n鬥技場:<br />\n每次要用一點對戰權<br />\n可挑戰其他玩家隊伍<br />\n對戰權每日三點回滿一次<br />\n會定期結算積分派英雄之翼<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n戰鬥系統:<br />\n同原作相比大同小異<br />\n本作冇命中率閃避率<br />\n等級高過對手5lv.時唔會有經驗值<br />\n攻方速度比守方大於5時可以發動追擊<br />\n兵種:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8r2ts8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8r2ts8E.png&h=350736b9&s={SIZE}\" />步行系 可行2格 可走入樹林,行1格<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYe7i0H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYe7i0H.png&h=a9612841&s={SIZE}\" />重裝系 可行1格 守備值較高<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm3927a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm3927a.png&h=06c88334&s={SIZE}\" />騎馬系 可行3格 入唔到樹林<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3O0f3c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3O0f3c0.png&h=aac6246f&s={SIZE}\" />飛行系 可行2格 會被弓剋制 可飛過樹林,山同河<br />\n兵器:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>屬(劍/魔法/石)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span>屬(斧/魔法/石)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>屬(槍/魔法/石)<br />\n無屬(弓/暗器/杖)<br />\n<br />\n相剋:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span>&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span><br />\n另外部份角色持有剋制個別兵種嘅武器<br />\n例如剋重裝系嘅劍/槌(斧), 對暗器發動追擊嘅弓, 對龍系特效嘅ファルシオン(Falchion)同封印之劍(Binding Blade)etc.<br />\n個體修正/ 成長值:<br />\n就算係相同既角色, 都會有唔同既個體修正, 但係每個相同角色既成長比例都會係一樣, 升級時能力值提升並非隨機。<br />\n個體修正只有三個可能性:<br />\n1. 提升兩項能力, 減低兩項能力, 一項能力正常<br />\n2. 提升一項能力, 減低一項能力, 三項能力正常<br />\n3. 全部能力都正常<br />\n以チキ(紋章)為例, 等級一的能力為HP15, 攻21, 速4, 守8, 魔防6<br />\n我地比對數據就知道, チキ(紋章)既個體修正係加攻擊減魔防, 升到40級既能力一定係HP41, 攻49, 速30, 守32, 魔防25<br />\n關於各角色既個體修正, 可以查呢個網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://fireemblem.gamewith.jp/article/show/51352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffireemblem.gamewith.jp%2Farticle%2Fshow%2F51352&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ce85290f\" target=\"_blank\">https://fireemblem.gamewith.jp/article/show/51352</a><br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n刷首抽 iOS要del app重裝, An要清data<br />\n建議打完教學後可以打埋序章先5連抽<br />\n又易打又快完<br />\n唔想打既就最多4連抽<br />\n<br />\n推薦首抽角色:<br />\nFANS向嘅GAME有5星就屌啦<br />\n真係想追嘅話<br />\n現時為止以下角色只有5星:<br />\nチキ (紋章)<br />\nミネルバ<br />\nリンダ<br />\nリン<br />\nヘクトル<br />\nリオン<br />\nルキナ<br />\nアクア<br />\nリョウマ<br />\nヒノカ<br />\nタクミ<br />\nレオン<br />\nエリーゼ<br />\n覺醒:<br />\n全GAME角色都可以經覺醒上5星<br />\n<strong>覺醒後會重設限界突破</strong><br />\n覺醒需要該角色屬性嘅系勳章/大勳章同英雄之翼<br />\n而4星升5星要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">20000英雄之翼</span><br />\n加上覺醒上5星同抽返黎就5星嘅能力其實冇分別<br />\n所以有錢就追5星<br />\n冇錢嘅唔追都冇問題不過就要好耐先升到一隻<br />\n限界突破:<br />\n食同星或以上嘅同款角色會額外+1(註:唔係升1lv.)<br />\n例如:<br />\nLv.20嘅4星食左4/5星嘅自己<br />\n就會變成Lv.20+1嘅4星<br />\nLv.20+1嘅4星覺醒後會變左Lv.1嘅5星<br />\n但係Lv.20嘅4星食左1-3星嘅自己就只會加SP(學技用)<br />\n所以最理想係用5星食自己5星<br />\n5星以下嘅你賣又得食黎+SP學技又得留黎自用都得<br />\n已確認數據: 加10角色係全能力+4 (最好疊加最靚個體修正個隻)"},{"pid":"d3c2c283a667907bfbdcf0aec5249241092a3ec8","tid":165383,"uid":38888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"Ios仲係得日本down到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}